sans-serif; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">Eligible candidates can apply online through official website of the university.</p>', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1, 1),
(3, 12, 0, '2014-02-27', '0000-00-00', 0, 0, 0, '', 'iit-delhi-notified-admission-to-a-part-time-mba-program-for-working-executives.html', 'IIT-Delhi Notified Admission to a PART-Time MBA Program for Working Executives', '<p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">Department of Management Studies, Indian Institute of Technology, Delhi (IITD), has invited applications for Admission to MBA (Part-Time/Evening) Program for working executives, focusing mainly on Technology Management.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;"><strong style="border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;"><span style="border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important; text-decoration: underline;">Important Dates</span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul style="margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style: none; border: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; text-align: justify; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius