 none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;"><strong style="border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">Course Duration:</strong>&nbsp;3 years</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;"><strong style="border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">Course focus on:</strong>&nbsp;Technology Management</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;"><strong style="border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">Classes Duration</strong>: Evening Batch - 6:15p.m. onwards, 4-5 working days (Monday to Friday)</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;"><strong style="border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">Eligibility Criteria:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol style="margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style: none inside; border: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; text-align: justify; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">\r\n	<li style="margin: 7px 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; list-style: decimal outside none; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">Bachelor&#39;s degree in any branch of Engineering / Technology / Architecture / Pharmacy / B.Sc. (AgriculturalEngineering) [Minimum 4 years after 10+2]<strong style="border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">&nbsp;OR</strong>&nbsp;Master&#39;s degree in any branch of Physical / Chemical / Mathematical Sciences like Physics, Chemistry,&nbsp;Mathematics, Statistics, Computer Applications, Electronic Science, Environmental Science, Operations&nbsp;Research, Computational / Information Science, Agriculture or Master&#39;s Degree in Commerce / Economics, CA&nbsp;/ ICWAI.</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 7px 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; list-style: decimal outside none; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">Minimum of 60% marks in aggregate (Cumulative for all the years / semesters) or 6.75 CGPA on a 10 point scale or equivalent in the above mentioned degree program.</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 7px 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; list-style: decimal outside none; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">There is a relaxation of 5% in marks or equivalent in CGPA for SC/ST candidates.</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 7px 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; list-style: decimal outside none; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">A minimum of 2 years of post-qualifying degree work experience as on 01 August 2014.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;"><strong style="border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">Selection Process:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul style="margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style: none; border: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; text-align: justify; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">\r\n	<li style="margin: 7px 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; list-style: inside url(http://www.jagranjosh.com/Resources/edu2/images/article_bullet.gif); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">IITD Part-Time MBA 2013 Admission Process: includes a Written Test, Group Discussion and Personal Interview.</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 7px 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; list-style: inside url(http://www.jagranjosh.com/Resources/edu2/images/article_bullet.gif); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">Weightage will be given to professional background in terms of higher performance in the qualifying degree/diplomas and work experience.</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 7px 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; list-style: inside url(http://www.jagranjosh.com/Resources/edu2/images/article_bullet.gif); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">Written Test is designed in four components to assess Verbal, Analytical, Quantitative / Data Interpretation abilities and Business Awareness.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;"><strong style=