(4, 12, 0, '2014-02-27', '0000-00-00', 0, 0, 0, '', 'imt-ghaziabad-announced-admission-for-pgdm-and-mba-programs-2014.html', 'IMT Ghaziabad announced admission for PGDM and MBA programs 2014', '<p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">Institute of Management Technology (IMT), Ghaziabad invited applications from interested and eligible candidates for admission to PGDM and MBA programs 2014. The candidates are advised to send their application in the prescribed format before 31 January 2014.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;"><strong style="border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">Important Date</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;"><strong style="border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">Last date for submitting the Application