-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;" />\r\n&bull; Candidates appearing for the final year examination of Bachelor Degree examination may also apply.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;"><strong style="border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">How to Apply</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">Eligible candidates can apply online through official website: http://www.imt.edu/ before 31 January 2014.</p>\r\n', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1, 1),
(5, 12, 0, '2014-02-27', '0000-00-00', 0, 0, 0, '', 'isme,-bangalore-invites-applications-for-pgdm-program.html', 'ISME, Bangalore Invites Applications for PGDM Program', '<p style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 1.4; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''Lucida Grande'', Verdana, ''Lucida Sans Regular'', ''Lucida Sans Unicode'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;">Applications are invited by&nbsp;<a href="http://member.minglebox.com/college/International-School-of-Management-Excellence-Bangalore" style="color: rgb(27, 93, 137) !important; text-decoration: none;"><strong>International School of Management Excellence (ISME), Bangalore</strong></a>&nbsp;for admission to AICTE approved Post Graduate Diploma in Management (PGDM) program for the commencing session 2014-16. Additionally students have an opportunity to visit&nbsp;<strong><a href="http://member.minglebox.com/college/London-School-of-Economics-and-Political-Science" style="color: rgb(27, 93, 137) !important; text-decoration: none;">London School of Economics (LSE), UK</a></strong>&nbsp;summer school between the first and second year.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 1.4; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''Lucida Grande'', Verdana, ''Lucida Sans Regular'', ''Lucida Sans Unicode'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;"><strong>Eligibility Criteria for ISME, Bangalore:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 25px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''Lucida Grande'', Verdana, ''Lucida Sans Regular'', ''Lucida Sans Unicode'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;">Students seeking admission to one of the above programs should have passed bachelor/ master degree examination of any recognized education body in Commerce, Management, Arts, Science, and Engineering, Technology or equivalent with a minimum of 50% aggregate marks.</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;">Candidates should also have appeared for one of the Management Aptitude Tests and performed well on the test.</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;">Work experience will be an important consideration for admissions.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 1.4; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''Lucida Grande'', Verdana, ''Lucida Sans Regular'', ''Lucida Sans Unicode'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;"><strong>How to Apply for ISME, Bangalore:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 25px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''Lucida Grande'', Verdana, ''Lucida Sans Regular'', ''Lucida Sans Unicode'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;">Completed application can be downloaded from the website.</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;">Resume</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;">Copy of official academic transcripts/marks card for graduate degree, 12th standard and 10th standard examination.</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;">Statement of Purpose.</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;">CAT/GMAT/CMAT/XAT test score.</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;"><strong>Application Fee:</strong>&nbsp;Demand Draft for Rs. 1000/- made in favour of &quot;International School of Management Excellence&quot; payable at Bangalore.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 1.4; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''Lucida Grande'', Verdana, ''Lucida Sans Regular'', ''Lucida Sans Unicode'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;">For more details and information on application procedure, please visit<strong><a href="http://www.isme.in/" style="color: rgb(27, 93, 137) !important; text-decoration: none;" target="_blank">www.isme.in</a></strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 1.4; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''Lucida Grande'', Verdana, ''Lucida Sans Regular'', ''Lucida Sans Unicode'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;" text-align:=""><strong>Also, the application can be obtained in one of the following ways -</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 25px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''Lucida Grande'', Verdana, ''Lucida Sans Regular'', ''Lucida Sans Unicode'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;">Registering on this website and downloading the application form.</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;">Write to the admission co-ordinator (at ISME address) with a cheque/demand draft for Rs. 1000/- made in favor of &quot;International School of Management Excellence&quot; payable at Bangalore.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 1.4; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''Lucida Grande'', Verdana, ''Lucida Sans Regular'', ''Lucida Sans Unicode'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;"><strong>Selection Procedure for ISME, Bangalore:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 1.4; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''Lucida Grande'', Verdana, ''Lucida Sans Regular'', ''Lucida Sans Unicode'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;">Completed application information</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 1.4; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''Lucida Grande'', Verdana, ''Lucida Sans Regular'', ''Lucida Sans Unicode'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;"><strong>Note:</strong>&nbsp;The school cannot begin to review an application until all parts have been received.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 1.4; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''Lucida Grande'', Verdana, ''Lucida Sans Regular'', ''Lucida Sans Unicode'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;">The completed application should be sent to the ISME admission office: International School of Management Excellence, CAP 1, EOIZ, Export Promotion Industrial Park, Near ITPL, Whitefield, Bangalore - 560066.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 1.4; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''Lucida Grande'', Verdana, ''Lucida Sans Regular'', ''Lucida Sans Unicode'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;"><strong>Interviews:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 1.4; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''Lucida Grande'', Verdana, ''Lucida Sans Regular'', ''Lucida Sans Unicode'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;">You will be called for an interview with a panel of experts if the school feels that you have a strong potential to be a successful candidate. These interviews will be held during&nbsp;<strong>February, March, April and May</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 1.4; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''Lucida Grande'', Verdana, ''Lucida Sans Regular'', ''Lucida Sans Unicode'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;"><strong>Admissions Decision:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 1.4; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''Lucida Grande'', Verdana, ''Lucida Sans Regular'', ''Lucida Sans Unicode'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;">Admission to the programs is highly competitive. The Admissions Office reviews applications on an individual basis looking at both quantitative and qualitative aspects of an applicant&#39;s professional and academic background. The committee seeks to assess an individual&#39;s potential for academic success and future professional growth.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 1.4; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''Lucida Grande'', Verdana, ''Lucida Sans Regular'', ''Lucida Sans Unicode'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;">The admissions committee will carefully consider each completed application, with particular attention to academic performance in school and graduation, test scores, work history, extracurricular and community activities and honors and achievements and personal essay. Personal characteristics that add to the diversity of the class may also be considered.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 1.4; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''Lucida Grande'', Verdana, ''Lucida Sans Regular'', ''Lucida Sans Unicode'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;">In general, candidates applying before the round 1 deadline will receive a decision during the end of March; those applying before the round two deadline will receive a decision by the end of April and those applying by the round three deadline will receive a decision by the end of May.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 1.4; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''Lucida Grande'', Verdana, ''Lucida Sans Regular'', ''Lucida Sans Unicode'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;"><strong>Important Dates:</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 1.4; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''Lucida Grande'', Verdana, ''Lucida Sans Regular'', ''Lucida Sans Unicode'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;">ISME, Bangalore employs a rolling admissions process--meaning all applications are generally reviewed in chronological order according to the date they were completed. Please note that these dates are not absolute deadlines.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 1.4; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''Lucida Grande'', Verdana, ''Lucida Sans Regular'', ''Lucida Sans Unicode'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;">It is to each applicant&#39;s benefit to apply earlier rather than later, but the school encourages applicants to submit the strongest application of which they are capable. They continue offering admission until they believe the incoming class to be full.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 5px 0px; padding: 5px 0px; line-height: 1.4; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''Lucida Grande'', Verdana, ''Lucida Sans Regular'', ''Lucida Sans Unicode'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify;"><strong>Application Deadline (July Batch) starting end of July, 2014</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 25px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''Lucida Grande'', Verdana, ''Lucida Sans Regular'', ''Lucida Sans Unicode'', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 18px;">\r\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;">Round 1 Deadline:<strong>&nbsp;Saturday, January 25, 2014.</strong></li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;">Round 2 Deadline:&nbsp;<strong>Friday, February 28, 2014.</strong></li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify;">Round 3 Deadline:<strong>&nbsp;Tuesday, April 15, 2014.</strong></li>\r\n</ul>', '', '', '', '', '', '', 0, 1, 1);
