(6, 13, 13, '2014-02-07', '2013-10-31', 2, 3, 1416543212, '1-1A, City Pulse Mall, Narayan Singh Circle, Tonk Road, Jaipur- 302004', 'naarm-announced-admission-notification-for-pgdma-2014-16.html', 'NAARM announced admission notification for PGDMA 2014-16', '<p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">National Academy of Agricultural Research Management (NAARM) invited applications for admission to<strong style="border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">&nbsp;</strong>Post Graduate Diploma in Management Agriculture (PGDMA 2014-16). NAARM is one of the premier Agricultural Research and management academies and was established by the Indian Council of Agricultural Research (ICAR) at Hyderabad in 1976.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;"><strong style="border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">Important Dates</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul style="margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style: none; border: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; text-align: justify; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">\r\n	<li style="margin: 7px 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; list-style: inside url(http://www.jagranjosh.com/Resources/edu2/images/article_bullet.gif); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;"><strong style="border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">Last Date for Receipt of Application forms: 28 February 2014</strong></li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 7px 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; list-style: inside url(http://www.jagranjosh.com/Resources/edu2/images/article_bullet.gif); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">Date of Dispatch of letters to Short-list Candidates: 15 March 2014</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 7px 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; list-style: inside url(http://www.jagranjosh.com/Resources/edu2/images/article_bullet.gif); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">Interview week (GD/PI): 20-25 May 2014</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 7px 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; list-style: inside url(http://www.jagranjosh.com/Resources/edu2/images/article_bullet.gif); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">Date of Declaration of Results: 31 May 2014</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;"><strong style="border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">Name of the</strong><strong style="border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">&nbsp;Programme:</strong>&nbsp;Post Graduate Diploma in Management Agriculture (PGDMA 2014-16)</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;"><strong style="border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">Total no. of Seats:&nbsp;</strong>30</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;"><strong style="border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">Eligibility Criteria for Admission</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">Candidate should have four year bachelor&rsquo;s degree from any Agricultural University or Institution recognized by the ICAR / UGC in Agriculture, Agri-Business Management/ Commercial Agriculture, Agricultural Marketing and Cooperation, Agricultural Engineering, Agricultural Information Technology, Agricultural Bioinformatics, Agricultural Biotechnology, Dairy Science/Technology, Fisheries, Food Technology/Food Process Engineering, Forestry, Horticulture, Sericulture and Veterinary Sciences.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;"><strong style="border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">Application Fee</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">Candidates need to pay application fee of Rs.500/-<strong style="border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">&nbsp;</strong>(Rs.300/-for SC/ST) in favour of &quot;ICAR-Unit, NAARM A/C&quot; and payable at Hyderabad.<strong style="border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;"><strong style="border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">Selection Criteria</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">Candidate&rsquo;s selection for admission to the courses will be made on the basis of scores obtained in CAT, group discussion, personal interview and academic record.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; border: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;"><strong style="border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">How to Apply</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul style="margin: 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style: none; border: 0px; outline: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; text-align: justify; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">\r\n	<li style="margin: 7px 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; list-style: inside url(http://www.jagranjosh.com/Resources/edu2/images/article_bullet.gif); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">Candidates are required to apply online through website of the institute&nbsp;<a href="http://www.naarm.ernet.in/" rel="nofollow" style="color: rgb(54, 80, 147); text-decoration: none; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important; border: 0px; outline: none; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">www.naarm.ernet.in</a>.</li>\r\n	<li style="margin: 7px 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: none; list-style: inside url(http://www.jagranjosh.com/Resources/edu2/images/article_bullet.gif); font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; border-top-left-radius: 0px !important; border-top-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px !important; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px !important;">After submission of online application, candidates are required to take a printout of e-Application form and send hard copy of application a