(1, 9, 13, '2014-01-10', '2013-10-31', 2, 3, 1412395402, 'IIRM Campus, Tagore Marg, Mansarovar, Jaipur-302020, Rajasthan (India)', 'indian-institute-of-rural-management-(iirm).html', 'Indian Institute of Rural Management (IIRM)', '<p>Institute of Rural Management Anand (IRMA), Gujarat, is a renowned management institute in India. The college provides professional education to train managers for rural management of the country. IRMA is an autonomous institution incepted in &nbsp;the year 1979. The institute aims at the growth of the rural sector but the campus of the institute is equipped with all the conveniences which the students can utilize in order to have an enhanced understanding of the concepts of rural management.</p>\r\n', 'estd8855.jpg', '<p>Institute of Rural Management Anand (IRMA), Gujarat, is a renowned management institute in India. The college provides professional education to train managers for rural management of the country. IRMA is an autonomous institution incepted in &nbsp;the year 1979. The institute aims at the growth of the rural sector but the campus of the institute is equipped with all the conveniences which the students can utilize in order to have an enhanced understanding of the concepts of rural management.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Courses :-<br />\r\nPost Graduate Diploma in Management (Full Time)-PGDM<br />\r\nPGDM (Rural Marketing)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Campus :-<br />\r\nInstitute of Rural Management is spread across 60 acres of land.The library and the computer center of the institute open the gates of unlimited knowledge for the students. The hostel also maintains a mess which provides tasty and hygienic food and snacks. The lecture halls, seminar rooms and the auditorium facilitate in the communication between the students and the members of the faculty.</p>\r\n', '<p>Indian Institute of Rural Management (IIRM) Courses offered<br />\r\nPost Graduate Diploma in Management (Full Time)-PGDM<br />\r\nDuration:- 2 Years</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Eligibility:- Graduation in any discipline with minimum 50% marks</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Admission:- Admission based on MAT Score Merit list, group discussion and interview.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fees:- Rs. 4,44,500/-</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Post Graduate Diploma in Management - Rural Management (PGDMRM)<br />\r\nDuration:- 2 Years</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Eligibility:- Graduation in any discipline with minimum 50% marks</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Admission:- Admission based on MAT Score Merit list, group discussion and interview.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fees:- Rs. 4,44,500/-</p>\r\n', 'Indian Institute of Rural Management (IIRM)', 'Indian Institute of Rural Management (IIRM)', 'indian institute of rural management (iirm)', 0, 1, 1),
(2, 9, 13, '2014-01-10', '2013-10-30', 2, 3, 1416500000, 'AB 559, Kings Road, Nirman Nagar, Jaipur, Rajasthan, India.', 'taxila-business-school.html', 'Taxila Business School', '<p>Taxila Business School for Business Studies is today ranked among the top business schools in the country, which is situated in the prestigious corporate area of Jaipur. Taxila aims to provide an education system that looks beyond employment and concentrates on foundation of lifetime for professional and personal development. Taxila Business School is &nbsp;a college and authorised academic college of IASE University Rajasthan and is &nbsp;authorised to run MBA. TAXILA provides Dual program &ndash; PGDBM (Autonomus) from Taxila Business School along with MBA Degree from &nbsp; IASE UNIVERSITY Rajasthan an UGC recognized University and Dual specialization in Marketing, Finance, Human Resources, International Business, Information Technology &amp; Retail Management . TAXILA&rsquo;s main commitment is to provide an excellent quality management education and all-round personality development, through research driven faculty both from pure academics and industry. TAXILA&rsquo;s teaching methodology strikes a perfect chord between theory and practice. It includes lectures and presentations, seminars, guest lectures and industry visits. To be successful in a changing global economy, managers must view the total enterprise and understand the forces shaping the firm&rsquo;s direction, policies, and goals and at the same time exercise personal leadership in managing employees. TAXILA applies basic social science disciplines and research methods to these management and leadership problems in the public and private sectors.</p>\r\n', 'taxila1793.jpg', '<p>Taxila Business School for Business Studies is today ranked among the top business schools in the country, which is situated in the prestigious corporate area of Jaipur. Taxila aims to provide an education system that looks beyond employment and concentrates on foundation of lifetime for professional and personal development. Taxila Business School is &nbsp;a college and authorised academic college of IASE University Rajasthan and is &nbsp;authorised to run MBA. TAXILA provides Dual program &ndash; PGDBM (Autonomus) from Taxila Business School along with MBA Degree from &nbsp; IASE UNIVERSITY Rajasthan an UGC recognized University and Dual specialization in Marketing, Finance, Human Resources, International Business, Information Technology &amp; Retail Management . TAXILA&rsquo;s main commitment is to provide an excellent quality management education and all-round personality development, through research driven faculty both from pure academics and industry. TAXILA&rsquo;s teaching methodology strikes a perfect chord between theory and practice. It includes lectures and presentations, seminars, guest lectures and industry visits. To be successful in a changing global economy, managers must view the total enterprise and understand the forces shaping the firm&rsquo;s direction, policies, and goals and at the same time exercise personal leadership in managing employees. TAXILA applies basic social science disciplines and research methods to these management and leadership problems in the public and private sectors.</p>\r\n', '<p>Master of Business Administration (MBA) + Post Graduate Diploma in Business Management (PGDBM)<br />\r\nTaxila Business School&#39;s MBA+PGDBM Program is a truly distinctive academic experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>TBS general management focus offers students holistic exposure to business disciplines, empowering them with versatile skills to succeed at many levels. Opportunities abound for students to explore a variety of offerings, with courses in entrepreneurship, and social enterprise, as well as field-based learning that enriches their learning.<br />\r\nEligibility:-</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Students studying in their final year of graduation BBA/ BA/BSc/B.Com /BE /B.Tech/ LLb/ MBBS/ any degree equivalent to graduation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Students who have passed graduation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;Students who have passed MAT/TMAT are required to appear for group discussion and Interview.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MBA (Executive) + Executive Post Graduate Diploma in Business Management (EPGDBM)<br />\r\nThe Executive MBA + EPGDBM &nbsp;is &nbsp;an &nbsp;intensive &nbsp;Two &nbsp;year &nbsp;program &nbsp;designed &nbsp;to &nbsp;enhance &nbsp;skills &nbsp;and &nbsp;capabilities essential for responsible positions at senior management levels. To meet this gap, the EMBA program has a distinct focus on leadership skills essential for senior management teams and is adapted from best-practices in industry. The interdisciplinary nature of the program will enrich your experience both inside and outside the classrooms &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nAdmission Procedure:&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The programme is intended for executives having substantial work experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The pre- requisites are: &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Graduate in any discipline. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Two years full time work experience. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Achievements (Academic and career related) &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Personal Interview&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The admission process is highly personalized as the committee seeks to learn about each candidate&#39;s goals and potential for success in management</p>\r\n', 'Taxila Business School', '', 'taxila business school', 0, 1, 1),
(3, 9, 13, '2014-01-10', '2013-10-31', 2, 3, 1416543212, '1-1A, City Pulse Mall, Narayan Singh Circle, Tonk Road, Jaipur- 302004', 'nimt-group-of-institutions.html', 'NIMT Group of Institutions', '<p>NIMT Group of Institutions is one of the leading institute of management in India which was established in the year 1985. The international boundaries have shrunk today &amp; an integrated global economy is fast emerging. The corporate sectors &amp; business houses are facing challenge of international competition, which can only be taken care of through high quality management &amp; leadership. The crisis of contemporary societies is the crisis of good leadership. The motto of NIMT encompasses the provision of educational programmes which are relevant to the needs of society, industry, profession &amp; are appropriate for a major management &amp; or other professional institutions. Keeping in view these criteria, our management &amp; professional programmes are not only rigorous &amp; intensive in nature but have an international perspective. They are designed to equip aspiring professionals with required management &amp; other skills &amp; to the present as well as those of future, with confidence. The programmes offered by NIMT to aspiring professionals have all the ingredients that make a very significant contribution to their future career. The teaching methodology &amp; industry interface has been designed in such a way that an overall personality development of students is achieved.</p>\r\n', 'nimt147.jpg', '<p>NIMT Group of Institutions is one of the leading institute of management in India which was established in the year 1985. The international boundaries have shrunk today &amp; an integrated global economy is fast emerging. The corporate sectors &amp; business houses are facing challenge of international competition, which can only be taken care of through high quality management &amp; leadership. The crisis of contemporary societies is the crisis of good leadership. The motto of NIMT encompasses the provision of educational programmes which are relevant to the needs of society, industry, profession &amp; are appropriate for a major management &amp; or other professional institutions. Keeping in view these criteria, our management &amp; professional programmes are not only rigorous &amp; intensive in nature but have an international perspective. They are designed to equip aspiring professionals with required management &amp; other skills &amp; to the present as well as those of future, with confidence. The programmes offered by NIMT to aspiring professionals have all the ingredients that make a very significant contribution to their future career. The teaching methodology &amp; industry interface has been designed in such a way that an overall personality development of students is achieved.</p>\r\n', '<p>NIMT Group of Institutions Courses offered<br />\r\nMaster of Business Administration (MBA)<br />\r\nThe program Technology, Kotputli, Jaipur. B.Tech (pproved by AICTE, Ministry of HRD and Affilated to Rajasthan Technical University/</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Duration:- 2 years</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Eligibility:- Graduation in any stream with minimum 60% marks (45% for sc/st)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Selection Procedure:- Admission on the basis of the marks of CAT/MAT/XAT/AIMA/ATMA/GMAT/AIM-CAT and GD/PI</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Post Graduate Diploma In Management (PGDM)<br />\r\nDuration:- 2 years</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Eligibility:- Graduation in any stream with minimum 50% marks (45% for sc/st)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Selection Procedure:- Admission on the basis of the marks of CAT/MAT/XAT/AIMA/ATMA/GMAT/AIM-CAT and GD/PI</p>\r\n', 'NIMT Group of Institutions', '', 'nimt group of institutions', 0, 1, 1),
(4, 9, 13, '2014-01-10', '0000-00-00', 0, 0, 1412795111, 'Bambala, Kota Road, Jaipur-302033 (Rajasthan)', 'ccs-national-institute-of-agricultural-marketing-(niam).html', 'CCS National Institute of Agricultural Marketing (NIAM)', '<p>The CCS National Institute of Agricultural Marketing (NIAM) is one of the best institute of management in Jaipur which is a premier National level Institute set up by the Government of India in August 1988 to offer specialized Training, Research, Consultancy and Education in Agricultural Marketing. NIAM is an autonomous body under the aegis of the Ministry of Agriculture, Government of India. It was set up as a Registered Society to cater to the needs of Agricultural Marketing personnel in India as well as from South East Asian countries. The Union Minister for Agriculture is the President of the General body of NIAM and Secretary, Department of Agriculture and Cooperation is the Chairman of the Executive Committee. The Campus of the National Institute of Agricultural Marketing is situated m a 33 acre plot of land on the outskirts of Jaipur City. The Campus is on National Highway No.12 connecting Jaipur with Kota</p>\r\n', 'niam9397.jpg', '<p>The CCS National Institute of Agricultural Marketing (NIAM) is one of the best institute of management in Jaipur which is a premier National level Institute set up by the Government of India in August 1988 to offer specialized Training, Research, Consultancy and Education in Agricultural Marketing. NIAM is an autonomous body under the aegis of the Ministry of Agriculture, Government of India. It was set up as a Registered Society to cater to the needs of Agricultural Marketing personnel in India as well as from South East Asian countries. The Union Minister for Agriculture is the President of the General body of NIAM and Secretary, Department of Agriculture and Cooperation is the Chairman of the Executive Committee. The Campus of the National Institute of Agricultural Marketing is situated m a 33 acre plot of land on the outskirts of Jaipur City. The Campus is on National Highway No.12 connecting Jaipur with Kota</p>\r\n', '<p>CCS National Institute of Agricultural Marketing (NIAM) Courses offered<br />\r\nPost Graduate Diploma in Agri-Business Management (PGDABM)<br />\r\nThe Post Graduate Diploma in Agri-Business Management combines the best of MBA with unique skills required for a career in Agri-Business.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Duration:- 2 years</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Eligibility:- Graduation</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Selection Procedure:-<br />\r\nAll India entrance test NIAMAT conducted which covers quantitative analysis, data interpretation, English, Agriculture &amp; social awareness questions. On the basis of written test students are finalized. The final test comprises group discussion/case studies, extempore and personal interview. Thus after a rigorous procedure a student is selected for PGDABM at NIAM.</p>\r\n', 'CCS National Institute of Agricultural Marketing (NIAM)', 'CCS National Institute of Agricultural Marketing (NIAM)', 'ccs national institute of agricultural marketing (niam)', 0, 1, 1),
(5, 9, 13, '2014-01-10', '0000-00-00', 0, 0, 1412784311, 'Sector 7, Madhyam Marg, Mansarovar Jaipur - 302020, Rajasthan.', 'maharishi-arvind-institute-of-engineering-technology.html', 'Maharishi Arvind Institute of Engineering Technology', '<p>MAIET is a pioneer self-financed institute, established in 1999 in the State of Rajasthan. The institute is spread over 6 acres of land in a lushgreen campus in the posh and modern locality of Mansarovar, Jaipur. Railway station and Bus stand (Sindhi Camp) are in the range of 8-9 Kms. from the college and are connected through fast and frequent transport facilities round the clock.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The management and faculty are fully committed to generate excellence in academics and to attain the sacred goal of making the students realize their full potential in all dimensions of their personality.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Academic performance of our students has been constantly outstanding and a significant number of students have secured distinctions/positions at the University level examinations.</p>\r\n', '633881743067263905ma3577.jpg', '<p>MAIET is a pioneer self-financed institute, established in 1999 in the State of Rajasthan. The institute is spread over 6 acres of land in a lushgreen campus in the posh and modern locality of Mansarovar, Jaipur. Railway station and Bus stand (Sindhi Camp) are in the range of 8-9 Kms. from the college and are connected through fast and frequent transport facilities round the clock.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The management and faculty are fully committed to generate excellence in academics and to attain the sacred goal of making the students realize their full potential in all dimensions of their personality.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Academic performance of our students has been constantly outstanding and a significant number of students have secured distinctions/positions at the University level examinations.</p>\r\n', '<p>Course Affiliation: Rajasthan Technical University ,Kota Duration :- 2 years Specialization: HR Finance Marketing Eligibility:- The candidate should have passed Graduation in any discipline or 3 years recognized diploma (after 10+2) or equivalent from any recognized board with minimum 50% aggregate. Mode of Study :- Full Time, Regular Intake:- 60 Seats. Fees Structure:- NA -</p>\r\n', 'Maharishi Arvind Institute of Engineering & Technology', 'Maharishi Arvind Institute of Engineering & Technology', 'maharishi arvind institute of engineering technology', 0, 1, 1),
(6, 9, 13, '2014-01-10', '0000-00-00', 0, 0, 9414303754, 'E-6 RIICO Industrial Area, Tonk Road, Jaipur-302022 Tel No. 0141-2770873, Mob. 9414303754 Fax No. 0141-2771500', 'mkm-institute-of-management.html', 'MKM Institute of Management', '<p>MKM Institute of Management, is approved by A.I.C.T.E, New Delhi and is affiliated to University of Rajasthan, &nbsp;Technical University Kota, Hisar &amp; Berkley University, USA It is the first Non-Govt. Management Institute in Rajasthan located in the heart of Heritage city, Jaipur, EPIP, RIICO Industrial Area, Sitapura, Jaipur. EXCELLENT INFRASTRUCTURE In appreciation of this Magnum Scale and Grandeur contribution, the D.G. of MKM was adjudged the &nbsp;&ldquo;OUTSTANDING CITIZEN OF INDIA&rdquo; and awarded &ldquo;GEM OF INDIA AWARD &ndash;2004&rdquo; for his excellent management of this institute. MKM was awarded the National Award &ldquo;Arch of Excellence (Management Education- 2005)&rdquo; by the Hon&rsquo;ble Union Minister &nbsp; M. V. Rajashekharan in recognition of outstanding contribution in the field of Management Education, Quality teaching, best University results and cent percent placement in highly reputed National &amp; International Companies. MKM is the recipient of &ldquo;Indira Gandhi Priyadarshini Man of the year Award - 2004&rdquo; in the field of Education</p>', '633923817294103995mkm-im8088.jpg', '<p>MKM Institute of Management, is approved by A.I.C.T.E, New Delhi and is affiliated to University of Rajasthan, &nbsp;Technical University Kota, Hisar &amp; Berkley University, USA It is the first Non-Govt. Management Institute in Rajasthan located in the heart of Heritage city, Jaipur, EPIP, RIICO Industrial Area, Sitapura, Jaipur. EXCELLENT INFRASTRUCTURE In appreciation of this Magnum Scale and Grandeur contribution, the D.G. of MKM was adjudged the &nbsp;&ldquo;OUTSTANDING CITIZEN OF INDIA&rdquo; and awarded &ldquo;GEM OF INDIA AWARD &ndash;2004&rdquo; for his excellent management of this institute. MKM was awarded the National Award &ldquo;Arch of Excellence (Management Education- 2005)&rdquo; by the Hon&rsquo;ble Union Minister &nbsp; M. V. Rajashekharan in recognition of outstanding contribution in the field of Management Education, Quality teaching, best University results and cent percent placement in highly reputed National &amp; International Companies. MKM is the recipient of &ldquo;Indira Gandhi Priyadarshini Man of the year Award - 2004&rdquo; in the field of Education</p>', '<p>Master of Business Administration (MBA)<br />\r\nThe full time two-year programme (Four semesters) leads to MBA degree from the University of Rajasthan. The first year of the programme aims at familiarising the students with the foundational and functional aspects of the core courses. It also takes care of the specialised knowledge within the functional areas to develop a realistic understanding of the discipline and inculcate communication skills. The second year (III semester onwards) is devoted to the study of specialized subjets of management. Student is free to choose his specialization subject.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Eligibility &amp; Admission:-</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The minimum requirement for the admission to the programme is a three-year bachelor&rsquo;s degree (or equivalent) in any discipline, recognized by the association of Indian Universities with at least 50% aggregate marks. A written test is conducted under auspices of RMAT/CAT/MAT. Those who qualify in the written exam and come in the merit are eligible to be called for group discussion (GD) and personal interview (PI). The final decision regarding admission is made according to merit, as determined by RMAT based on the performance in the written test, GD &amp; PI. Students with less than 50% aggregate marks can also apply in MAT category.&nbsp;</p>', 'MKM Institute of Management', 'MKM Institute of Management', '', 0, 1, 1),
(7, 9, 13, '2014-01-10', '0000-00-00', 0, 0, 1412752240, '6-E, Malviya Industrial Area, Jaipur 302017', 'dr.-b.-lal-institute-of-biotechnology.html', 'Dr. B. Lal Institute of Biotechnology', '<p>Dr. B. Lal Institute of Biotechnology is one of &nbsp;the best college of management in Jaipur which imparts cosmopolitan atmosphere with experienced and learned teachers that strongly encourage and nurture students. &nbsp;It was established at the heart of the Jaipur city, at Malviya Nagar. The faculty is committed to strive hard for the overall development of tomorrow&rsquo;s professionals / biotechnologist.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Academic atmosphere offered at the institute is designed to incorporate a blend of knowledge, skills and the right attitude.</p>', '634152956530971885b-lala-biotechnology5355.jpg', '<p>Dr. B. Lal Institute of Biotechnology is one of &nbsp;the best college of management in Jaipur which imparts cosmopolitan atmosphere with experienced and learned teachers that strongly encourage and nurture students. &nbsp;It was established at the heart of the Jaipur city, at Malviya Nagar. The faculty is committed to strive hard for the overall development of tomorrow&rsquo;s professionals / biotechnologist.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Academic atmosphere offered at the institute is designed to incorporate a blend of knowledge, skills and the right attitude.</p>', '<p>Dr. B. Lal Institute of Biotechnology Courses offered<br />\r\nMBA- Hospital Management<br />\r\nMBA (Hospital Management) is industry-specific program prepares executive with the knowledge and skills required to lead the industry. This program in hospital management is to train medical &amp; non-medical graduates to undertake a wider range of administrative and managerial responsibilities within hospital organizations.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>No. of Seats:30-40</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Duration:2 years</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Eligibility : Graduate in any stream from a recognized university.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fee Structure:- Rs.14000 /-per semester</p>', 