(8, 9, 13, '2014-01-10', '0000-00-00', 0, 0, 1412711349, 'Jawaharlal Nehru Marg, Jaipur 302004', 'r-a-podar-institute-of-management.html', 'R A Podar Institute of Management', '<p>R. A Podar Institute of Management is one of the best institute of management in Jaipur which was established in the year 2002. The institute has been ranked amongst the Top-10 University Departments all over the country by Outlook survey 2006. The University of Rajasthan has been awarded A+ accreditation by NAAC in year 2004 and also it has been placed in level 1 of A+ category B-Schools in the Business India Survey.</p>', '634928209574249233r.-a-podar-institute-of-management-logo7256.jpg', '<p>R. A Podar Institute of Management is one of the best institute of management in Jaipur which was established in the year 2002. The institute has been ranked amongst the Top-10 University Departments all over the country by Outlook survey 2006. The University of Rajasthan has been awarded A+ accreditation by NAAC in year 2004 and also it has been placed in level 1 of A+ category B-Schools in the Business India Survey.</p>', '<p>R. A Podar Institute of Management Courses offered<br />\r\nMBA (RMAT)<br />\r\nThe course places emphasis on management as an integral process requiring students to develop a macro view of economic, technological, cultural and political environment under which a business operates.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Duration:- 2 years</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Eligibility:- Graduate in any discipline</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Admission Criteria:- The admission to MBA(RMAT) is made through the RMAT entrance test conducted by Rajasthan Technical University, KOTA.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Intake:- 60</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MBA (Computer Aided Management)<br />\r\nMBA CAM provides students with a strong background in the concepts, tools and techniques for making computers as integral and productive component of all management functions and processes. The course is a right blends of advanced tools of contemporary IT and Management.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Duration:- 2 years</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Eligibility:- Graduate in any discipline</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Admission Criteria:- The admission to MBA(RMAT) is made through the PIM- MAT entrance test conducted by Rajasthan Technical University, KOTA.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Intake:- 30</p>\r\n\r\n<p>MBA (E-Commerce)<br />\r\nMBA programme in E-Commerce aims to provide insight of the industrial world to the prospective managers.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Duration:- 2 years</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Eligibility:- Graduate in any discipline</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Admission Criteria:- The admission to MBA(RMAT) is made through the PIM- MAT entrance test conducted by Rajasthan Technical University, KOTA. + roup Discussion and Personal Intervie</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Intake:- 30</p>', 'R A Podar Institute of Management', 'R A Podar Institute of Management', 'r a podar institute of management', 0, 1, 1),
(9, 9, 13, '2014-01-10', '0000-00-00', 0, 0, 1412174351, 'ISI - 16, RIICO Institutional Complex, Kautilya Circle Sitapura, Jaipur - 302022 (Raj.) INDIA.', 'kautilya-institute-of-technology-and-engineering-and-school-of-management-(kite-som).html', 'Kautilya Institute of Technology and Engineering and School of Management (KITE-SOM)', '<p>Kautilya Institute of Technology and Engineering and School of Management (KITE-SOM) is one of the most prominent institute of management in Jaipur which empower students through education, training and to install confidence with a winning attitude. The institute endeavors is to provide best infrastructure and support system with emphasis on relevance in today&rsquo;s changing world, and provide both theory and practice needed for future career.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Institute is located in RIICO Institutional Complex, Sitapura, Jaipur. Which is at an easy approach from heart of the city. It is 8 km away from Airport circle, Sanganer, 11 km away from Durgapura Railway Station and is well connected with city bus service and other means of transport.&nbsp;</p>', '634175537848032273kite3836.jpg', '<p>Kautilya Institute of Technology and Engineering and School of Management (KITE-SOM) is one of the most prominent institute of management in Jaipur which empower students through education, training and to install confidence with a winning attitude. The institute endeavors is to provide best infrastructure and support system with emphasis on relevance in today&rsquo;s changing world, and provide both theory and practice needed for future career.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Institute is located in RIICO Institutional Complex, Sitapura, Jaipur. Which is at an easy approach from heart of the city. It is 8 km away from Airport circle, Sanganer, 11 km away from Durgapura Railway Station and is well connected with city bus service and other means of transport.&nbsp;</p>', '<p>Kautilya Institute of Technology and Engineering and School of Management (KITE-SOM) Courses offered<br />\r\nMBA<br />\r\nDuration:- 2 years</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Eligibility:-&nbsp;<br />\r\nGraduate with 50% aggregate marks.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Admission Criteria:-&nbsp;<br />\r\nAdmission through RMAT or MAT Score + Group Discuission &amp; Personal Interview.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fees:- Rs. 50,000/- p.a.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Seats:- 60.</p>', 'Kautilya Institute of Technology and Engineering and School of Management (KITE-SOM)', 'Kautilya Institute of Technology and Engineering and School of Management (KITE-SOM)', 'kautilya institute of technology and engineering and school of management (kite-som)', 0, 1, 1),
(10, 9, 13, '2014-01-10', '0000-00-00', 0, 0, 1412251087, 'Bhankrota, Ajmer Road,Jaipur - 302026', 'rajasthan-institute-of-engineering-and-technology.html', 'Rajasthan Institute of Engineering and Technology', '<p>Rajasthan Institute of Engineering and Technology is one of the most prestigious institute of management in Jaipur which was established in the year 2000 with the approval of All India Council for Technical Education(AICTE),Ministry of HRD, Govt. of India. The Rajasthan Institute of Engineering and Technology is being run under the aegis of &quot;Chandrawati Education Society&quot; which is in the field of education since 2000.The society is registered with the registrar of societies, Govt. of N.C.T. Delhi vide registration No.S.35514 of 1999,under societies registration Act. of 1860</p>', '634175542639736689riet-27697.jpg', '<p>Rajasthan Institute of Engineering and Technology is one of the most prestigious institute of management in Jaipur which was established in the year 2000 with the approval of All India Council for Technical Education(AICTE),Ministry of HRD, Govt. of India. The Rajasthan Institute of Engineering and Technology is being run under the aegis of &quot;Chandrawati Education Society&quot; which is in the field of education since 2000.The society is registered with the registrar of societies, Govt. of N.C.T. Delhi vide registration No.S.35514 of 1999,under societies registration Act. of 1860</p>', '<p>Rajasthan Institute of Engineering and Technology Courses offered<br />\r\nMBA<br />\r\nDuration:- 2 years</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Eligibility:-&nbsp;<br />\r\nGraduation in any stream with minimum 50 % marks (45% marks SC/ST/OBC).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Admission Criteria:-&nbsp;<br />\r\nAdmissions are based on marks obtained in the graduation and score in any entrance exams.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Seats:- 60</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fees:- Rs. 60,000/- Per Year.</p>', 'Rajasthan Institute of Engineering and Technology', 'Rajasthan Institute of Engineering and Technology', 'raja